    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>简介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《天鹅之歌》是一款温馨感人的解谜游戏。通过放置形状大小不一的音符，为音乐盒编写旋律并解开谜题。在帮助天鹅抵达终点的过程中，逐步揭开一个关于家人、失去与悲伤的动人故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265290/extras/f537ed481e3413a0b51719382dfdc206.poster.avif?t=1772008215\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265290/extras/f537ed481e3413a0b51719382dfdc206.webm?t=1772008215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265290/extras/f537ed481e3413a0b51719382dfdc206.mp4?t=1772008215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏机制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个谜题都是一段有待谱写的乐曲。将音符放置在音阶上，它们的位置将决定旋律播放时哪些平台会被激活。当你完成谱写后，转动发条，让音乐引导天鹅通过关卡。 精准的时机与周密的布局是解开谜题的关键。在解谜的过程中，一段动人的叙事将逐渐展开，讲述音乐盒制作者以及这只为其家人制作的音乐盒背后的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265290/extras/1b0beaa68afaa8df561c6aebd8b4c1c5.poster.avif?t=1772008215\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265290/extras/1b0beaa68afaa8df561c6aebd8b4c1c5.webm?t=1772008215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265290/extras/1b0beaa68afaa8df561c6aebd8b4c1c5.mp4?t=1772008215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事背景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你发现了一只古老而神秘的音乐盒，里面保存着许多个人物品。这是制作者的最后一件作品——他的“绝唱”（Swan Song），也是精心制作献给家人的一份纪念。 随着谜题逐渐解开，制作者的故事也在慢慢浮现。他的家人经历了什么？音乐盒中又隐藏着怎样的秘密？让音乐带领你揭开这段关于悲伤、回忆与遗憾的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265290/extras/65ff33b80f3a022d9c9cf88408cc8650.poster.avif?t=1772008215\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265290/extras/65ff33b80f3a022d9c9cf88408cc8650.webm?t=1772008215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265290/extras/65ff33b80f3a022d9c9cf88408cc8650.mp4?t=1772008215\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Translated by <i>Aliveee</i></p>",
